{
  "stem": "18770.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There is a hope that somehow America will become involved in the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the general feeling is that they probably won't because the sentiment in America is, you know, is not to join the war for most people.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when, when Pearl Harbor comes, I remember there'd be-- and America gets involved in the war, there's a feeling, oh, good, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now maybe something will happen-- that sort of a feeling.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, I remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Do you remember having any, any memories or any discussions about the, the Jews who were there already versus these immigrant Jews and some kind of separation or, I don't know, some tensions between--",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In New York, you mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, not really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't feel that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There, there was such a large influx of refugee Jews into the West Side at that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember that being the case.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember a couple of times once or twice in school as a kid having some kind of a minor-- and maybe not so minor traumatic experiences, like, with a teacher one day saying to me-- because I-- we had gone on an outing, and I think I dropped a piece of paper on the ground.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And sort of bawling me out in front of the class and saying, well, if you don't like it here, you know, you should go back where you came from, something brilliant like that.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The war?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mhm, mhm--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's a huge adjustment going on, probably harder in some way for my parents on a physical level than it is for my sister and me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They do not speak English.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
